title: CUTEosis with Vinny Guadagnino | Chris Distefano Presents: Chrissy Chaos | EP 25
description:
WELCOME to Chrissy Chaos! 


 


This episode Chrissy Chaos is chilling with Vinny Guadagnino AKA the Keto Gudio from the Jersey Shore! The two sex icons talk dieting, how it is to be part of the Jersey Shore crew and how reality TV can impact your life. CHAOS ALL DAY BABE!
